summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 3797, entitled "An Ordinance to license and regulate auctioneers, to provide penalties for the violation of the provisions of the same and to repeal Ordinances 2477 and 2658", approved May 7, 1895, and Ordinance No. 3879, approved July 19, 1895, amending Ordinance No. 3797.
